         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="The Production Order is released by an authorized employee before production begins. This opens the Production Order and allows the entry of actual data from the plant floor. The Production Order is used to track and record production activity. &#10;&#10;&#10;INDUSTRY SPECIFIC: Release the order to the manufacturing floor, following creation of production order. &#10;&#10;"/>
